# Upload filter for `railway up`. Railway uses THIS instead of .gitignore for uploads,
# so we deliberately re-include the gitignored internal seeding tools the agent needs at
# runtime — agent/scripts/mainnet_seed.py + agent/src/feedback.py (ERC-8004 giveFeedback /
# 8004scan) — while still excluding heavy/irrelevant trees. The Dockerfile's .dockerignore
# then keeps the built image lean. Without this file, .gitignore drops mainnet_seed.py and the
# demo rotation ImportErrors on boot (no new circles, no reputation → 8004scan freezes).
.git
miniapp
contracts/lib
contracts/out
contracts/cache
contracts/broadcast
docs
**/node_modules
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.log
.claude
agent/.mainnet_members.json
agent/.mainnet_e2e.json
agent/.self_session.json
